quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  4,171,"Maaku an Nulaa…óo, wi'anaa Annasaara'en yim…ìe Linjiila : "Wata on fantin ka diina mon, wata on wowlu e hoore Alla fii Annabi Iisaa si wanaa goonaga kan. Pellet, Mema-sella Iisaa …ìi…ó…óo Maryama on, ko Nulaa…óo Alla mo O Nuliri goonga, O Tagirii mo Daalol Makko ngol O Nuliri Jibriilu (yo o his) faade e Maryam, ngol woni : Laato, O Laatii. ∆äum ko wuttaandu ndu Alla Nuliri Jibriilu yo wuttu. Awa gom…óinee Alla e Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen dennda-ngal hara on senndaali …ìe, wata on wi'u : "Rewetee…ói …óin ko tati", ha…óitee gaay e kan haala fenaande ; ko …óum …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde on aduna e laakara. Anndee pellet, Alla ko Rewetee…óo Gooto, Senii…óo gaay e kafideede e …ìi…ó…óo ! Ko O Galo. Ko Kanko Woodani laamateeri kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni e majji. Alla Yonii Hoolor…óo."
  4,172,"Mema-sella …ìi…ó…óo Maryama on salataa o ha…óitaaki nde o laatotoo jeyaa…óo Alla, wanaa Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìe ∆Åa…ótinani mo …ìen. Honno jogitorton Iisaa rewe- tee…óo ?! Ko honno sirkoo…ìe …ìen kadi jogitorta Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen rewetee…ói ?! Kala non nefinanii- …óo rewugol Alla ngol, o townitanii …óum, pellet, Alla Moo…ìitoyay …ìe denndaangal faade ka Makko √ëalnde Darngal, O Yo…ìita kala e ko hanndi kon."
  4,173,"Si tawii ko …ìen gom…óim…ìe Alla e Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen, …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e e hoore no sari'a on yami- yamriri non, arma O Okka …ìe baraaji golle ma…ì…ìe …óen O ∆Åeydana …ìe immorde e ∆Åural Makko ngal. ∆Åeya townitii…ìe e rewugol Mo …óoftoo Mo, O Leptay …ìe lepte muusu…óe, …ìe he…ìoytaa gaanin Alla, gi…óo nafoowo …ìe, wanaa ballo du√±anoowo …ìe lorra."
  4,174,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe ! Gom…óii hujja arii e moo…óon immorde ka Joomi mon ; on le ko Muhammadu (jom kisiyee), Men Jippinii e moo…óon ndaygu …ìanngu ngu ; ngun woni ndee Al Qur'aanaare."
  4,175,"Si tawii ko …ìen gom…óim…ìe Alla …ìe jogitii Alquraana Jippinaande nden e Annabaajo ma…ì…ìe on, arma Alla Yumee …ìe, O Naada …ìe Aljanna, O ∆Åeydana …ìe njo…ìdi e darja, O Fewnira …ìe laawol focciingol ; ngol woni laawol Aljanna ngol."